title: San Onofre surfers getting tickets, road into surf beach still 'unsafe'
text: San Onofre surfers getting tickets, road into surf beach still 'unsafe' Jan. 10, 2017 Updated 1:32 p.m. 1 of 7 Surfers crowd the upper parking lot at San Onofre State Beach while the lower parking lot along the beach was closed on Jan. 4, 2017.
